<page>
    <title>About cl-libxml2</title>

    <div>
        <h2>Features:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Interfaces for tree manipulation (like cxml-stp)</li>
            <li>Interface for an HTML 4.0 non-verifying parser</li>
            <li>Specific APIs to process HTML tree, especially serialization</li>
            <li>XPath API</li>
            <li>XSLT API</li>
            <li>Custom URL resolvers</li>
            <li>XPath extension functions</li>
            <li>XSLT extension elements</li>
            <li>Translate libxml2 and libxslt errors to Lisp conditions</li>
            <li>iterate drivers for enumerate child nodes and etc.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</page>